      "raw_text": "### firefox-beta Uplift Approval Request\n- **User impact if declined**: Webcompat issues when pages are served without a content type, and they start with a <!--comment.  Note no space between !-- and the text.\nSee bug 2006569.\n- **Code covered by automated testing**: yes\n- **Fix verified in Nightly**: yes\n- **Needs manual QE test**: yes\n- **Steps to reproduce for manual QE testing**: See bug 2006569 comment 0\n- **Risk associated with taking this patch**: low\n- **Explanation of risk level**: Fixes a regression. Aligns Firefox sniffing of HTML with other browsers. Fix is really simple and behind a pref\n- **String changes made/needed**: none\n- **Is Android affected?**: yes",
      "count": 10,
      "text": "### firefox-beta Uplift Approval Request\n- **User impact if declined**: Webcompat issues when pages are served without a content type, and they start with a <!--comment.  Note no space between !-- and the text.\nSee bug 2006569.\n- **Code covered by automated testing**: yes\n- **Fix verified in Nightly**: yes\n- **Needs manual QE test**: yes\n- **Steps to reproduce for manual QE testing**: See bug 2006569 comment 0\n- **Risk associated with taking this patch**: low\n- **Explanation of risk level**: Fixes a regression. Aligns Firefox sniffing of HTML with other browsers. Fix is really simple and behind a pref\n- **String changes made/needed**: none\n- **Is Android affected?**: yes",
