    {
      "creation_time": "2026-01-23T10:58:35Z",
      "raw_text": "Reproduced the issue with Firefox 148.0a1 (2025-12-17) on Windows 11. The https://ghosttogether.net/change/password webpage is displayed in html code when opened.\nThe issue is verified fixed with Firefox 149.0a1 (2026-01-22) on Windows 11, macOS 15 and Ubuntu 24. While the `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` pref it's true (as default) the https://ghosttogether.net/change/password page is correctly displayed. Turning `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` will reproduce the issue again.",
      "reactions": {},
      "text": "Reproduced the issue with Firefox 148.0a1 (2025-12-17) on Windows 11. The https://ghosttogether.net/change/password webpage is displayed in html code when opened.\nThe issue is verified fixed with Firefox 149.0a1 (2026-01-22) on Windows 11, macOS 15 and Ubuntu 24. While the `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` pref it's true (as default) the https://ghosttogether.net/change/password page is correctly displayed. Turning `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` will reproduce the issue again.",
      "tags": [],
      "attachment_id": null,
      "author": "atrif@mozilla.com",
      "bug_id": 2011628,
