    {
      "is_private": false,
      "count": 14,
      "id": 17859496,
      "time": "2026-01-26T10:19:13Z",
      "author": "atrif@mozilla.com",
      "tags": [],
      "attachment_id": null,
      "bug_id": 2011628,
      "creator": "atrif@mozilla.com",
      "text": "Verified fixed with 148.0b7 (20260125090536) [build](https://treeherder.mozilla.org/jobs?repo=mozilla-beta&revision=423d51461928874ff1b1ea476c9b2aa2fa3ed3f3) on Windows 11, macOS 14 and Ubuntu 24.  While the `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` pref it's true (as default) the https://ghosttogether.net/change/password page is correctly displayed. Turning `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` to false will reproduce the issue again.",
      "creation_time": "2026-01-26T10:19:13Z",
      "reactions": {},
      "raw_text": "Verified fixed with 148.0b7 (20260125090536) [build](https://treeherder.mozilla.org/jobs?repo=mozilla-beta&revision=423d51461928874ff1b1ea476c9b2aa2fa3ed3f3) on Windows 11, macOS 14 and Ubuntu 24.  While the `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` pref it's true (as default) the https://ghosttogether.net/change/password page is correctly displayed. Turning `network.mimesniff.non_standard_html_comment` to false will reproduce the issue again."
